  "detailed_description": "Spelldash is a fast-paced FPS parkour game where you use elemental spells and environment to run through levels<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919240/extras/cac4d36410918be374f634e77feb84fb.poster.avif?t=1724106395\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919240/extras/cac4d36410918be374f634e77feb84fb.webm?t=1724106395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919240/extras/cac4d36410918be374f634e77feb84fb.mp4?t=1724106395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use environmental elements like jumpers, jump pads, wallrunning, speed pads, rocket jump pads, bubble jumps and more to traverse the levels quickest and the most creative way possible<br><br>Use fire, air, ice and lightning elements, all with unique usages to eliminate the enemies<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919240/extras/efd950b47badf08a8daa2e049be6c6b1.poster.avif?t=1724106395\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919240/extras/efd950b47badf08a8daa2e049be6c6b1.webm?t=1724106395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1919240/extras/efd950b47badf08a8daa2e049be6c6b1.mp4?t=1724106395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast paced, intense parkour action<br></li><li>Unique campaign, collectathon and challenge modes<br></li><li>Open ended levels that can be completed in many ways<br></li><li>4 different elemental spells to eliminate enemies<br></li><li>Many different abilities to traverse the levels in different ways<br></li><li>Stylized environments<br></li><li>Global leaderboards</li></ul>",
